author: Anita Kumar
title: Trump’s unspoken factor on reopening the economy: Politics
description: Many Trump aides and allies say an earlier restart could help the president in his reelection campaign — and they're telling the president that.
content:
Hanging over the health data, however, is the politics of the situation. And many of Trumps political allies and outside advisers believe they have the public increasingly on their side.
